{"id": 232049652, "title": "Jayant Chaudhary, a Jat leader from UP, takes oath as minister in Modi Cabinet", "text": "Rashtriya Lok Dal (RLD) chief Jayant Chaudhary was inducted into the new Cabinet formed after Prime Minister Narendra Modi took oath as Prime Minister of India for a record third term. His party, Rashtriya Lok Dal, had joined the National Democratic Alliance (NDA) in March 2024 before the Lok Sabha elections had kicked off. Born in 1978, Jayant Chaudhary comes from a political family. His grandfather, Chaudhary Charan Singh, was the fifth Prime Minister of India. His father, Ajit Singh, had served as a former minister.Who gets which ministry in Modi 3.0? Form your 'Dream Cabinet' and win prizes.link__elec{padding:0 0 12px} .link__elec div{margin-bottom:7px;}.link__elec a{color: var(--linkcolor); text-decoration: underline;font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:600;} Notably, Chaudhary Charan Singh was awarded the Bharat Ratna in February this year. Charan Singh also served as the Chief Minister of Uttar Pradesh twice and is remembered as a \"champion of farmers\".Hours after the announcement of the Bharat Ratna, Jayant Chaudhary confirmed his alliance with the BJP-led NDA.Jayant Chaudhary was part of the 15th Lok Sabha and had served as Mathura MP from 2009 to 2014. Chaudhary had contested the 2014 Lok Sabha elections from Mathura, but had lost to BJP candidate Hema Malini.He then contested the 2019 polls Baghpat but faced defeat at the hands of BJP candidate Dr Satyapal Singh.Jayant Chaudhary was elected to the Rajya Sabha in July 2022.He holds a B.Com. (Hons) degree along with an M.Sc. (Accounting and Finance). He graduated from Delhi University\u2019s Shri Venkateshwara College and London School of Economics and Political Science.Published By: Anuja JhaPublished On: Jun 9, 2024", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/jayant-chaudhary-rashtriya-lok-dal-narendra-modi-cabinet-2551017-2024-06-09\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/jayant-chaudhary-092018246-16x9_0.jpg?VersionId=GM3fhNN5XpnU_k8Qo35tjRBeHDM6JygY\"> </a> Jayant Chaudhary, a Jat leader from UP, takes oath as minister in Modi Cabinet", "url": "https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/jayant-chaudhary-rashtriya-lok-dal-narendra-modi-cabinet-2551017-2024-06-09", "image": "https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/jayant-chaudhary-092018246-16x9_0.jpg?VersionId=GM3fhNN5XpnU_k8Qo35tjRBeHDM6JygY?size=1280:720", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 15:42:36", "author": null, "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": 0.143}